description:
Abraham is integral to three faithsJudaism, Islam, and Christianityand his experience has inspired countless people over the ages. He received a message from God to move to Canaan, promising that his descendants would make a great nation. Tested to the utmost to sacrifice his son, he was faithful to God's leading and leaves a legacy for us today.
